// Optional per-developer overrides loaded by packages/engine/src/config/models.ts.
// JSONC: `//` line and `/* */` block comments are stripped before JSON.parse.
//
// Per-tier provider/model assignment lives in connections.json (managed via the
// Connections UI), not here. The loader reads only `effort` and `pricing`.
//
// Effort values below mirror the production defaults in models.ts; uncomment to
// override one. Pricing overrides are keyed by model ID and useful for adjusting
// cost calculations during testing without redeploying.

